content:
Hamburg | 27.02.2024 | On Sunday, February 25, the 49th General Assembly was held with the participation of the members of the Hamburg Association affiliated to Atiif. In the opening speech held at the General Assembly, which started with the stance of respect: “Our association has been continuing its activities uninterruptedly for 49 years since it has been opened. said. Following the reading and discussion of the activity, political and financial reports, the new term management and audit committee was elected. Especially in recent years, new members of the association activities have increased motivation.

The General Assembly ended with the slogan “Union Struggle Zafer, Long Long Atik YDG New Woman”.
